  "title": "JavaScript / jQuery HTML Elements",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "JavaScript / jQuery HTML Elements"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "jQuery vs JavaScript"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "jQuery was created in 2006 by John Resig. \nIt was designed to handle Browser Incompatibilities and to simplify HTML DOM Manipulation, Event Handling, Animations, and Ajax."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "However, after JavaScript Version 5 (2009), most of the jQuery utilities can be solved with a few lines of standard JavaScript:"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Set Text Content"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Set the inner text of an HTML element:"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "myElement.text(\"Hello Sweden!\");"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "myElement.textContent = \"Hello Sweden!\";"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Get Text Content"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Get the inner text of an HTML element:"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "myText = $(\"#02\").text();"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "myText = document.getElementById(\"02\").textContent;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Set HTML Content"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Set the HTML content of an element:"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "myElement.html(\"<p>Hello World</p>\");"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "myElement.innerHTML = \"<p>Hello World</p>\";"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Get HTML Content"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Get the HTML content of an element:"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "content = myElement.html();"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "content = myElement.innerHTML;"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}